WEBVTT

00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:02.566
I'll hit the restroom.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:07.733
Excuse me.

00:00:10.866 --> 00:00:12.466
What happened to him?

00:00:20.266 --> 00:00:21.700
How did that feel?

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:23.466
You like it?

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:29.500
Don't tell me

00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:30.500
that was

00:00:30.733 --> 00:00:31.800
part of the treatment!

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:34.100
I just wanted to see

00:00:34.100 --> 00:00:34.833
if any

00:00:34.833 --> 00:00:36.133
stimulation would

00:00:36.900 --> 00:00:38.233
make you better.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:39.600
If that

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:40.733
won't even work,

00:00:41.300 --> 00:00:42.200
we have to

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:43.466
go with meds.

00:00:44.933 --> 00:00:45.933
Stop lying!

00:00:46.833 --> 00:00:48.000
This is not treatment!

00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:52.500
For others, it's not.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:55.300
But you

00:00:57.500 --> 00:00:58.333
are different.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:03.933
Behave yourself!

00:01:12.866 --> 00:01:13.900
Your condition

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.233
is not serious.

00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:17.266
I can cure you

00:01:17.266 --> 00:01:18.066
within 3 months.

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:20.766
Remember to

00:01:20.766 --> 00:01:22.066
get the meds tomorrow.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:27.833
Wipe yourself.

00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:32.866
Close your eyes!

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:40.300
Wow.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:44.766
Whoa...

00:01:45.633 --> 00:01:46.533
Joseph?

00:01:50.033 --> 00:01:50.866
Jesus!

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:52.233
You and Charles!

00:01:52.633 --> 00:01:53.500
Wow!

